full_text:
Jordan Lynne Pruitt  is an American recording artist. After recording a demo album in 2006, Pruitt was signed to Hollywood Records.
Pruitt has released two albums, the debut No Ordinary Girl  followed by Permission to Fly . "Outside Looking In" is taken from the debut album, the song charted on the US Billboard 200. Pruitt is currently residing near Franklin, Tennessee and in Los Angeles, when not on tour, she is preparing to record her third album.
title: Jordan Pruitt
